### Aapko ab kya karna hai:
1. GitHub par apni repository **`sportsnap-pro`** me jao.
2. **`package.json`** file ko open karke edit (pencil icon) par click karo.
3. Purana code poora hatakar upar diya hua naya code paste kar do (isme humne node version `"24.x"` kar diya hai).
4. Neeche **"Commit changes"** par click karke save kar do.

Jaise hi aap commit karoge, Vercel automatic background me building start kar dega aur is baar bina kisi error ke successfully green check (✓) ke sath deploy ho jayega!
